{"tid":1988872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 中行「原油寶」虧300多億 投資者被逼跳樓","createTime":"2020-04-25T13:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T19:49:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"432db8cd4f83118656b1888e239ebe25d1a0118e","tid":1988872,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"家住廣東的趙先生對自由亞洲表示，他不僅6萬元本金血本無歸，還倒欠銀行13萬元。上海劉先生原本投資33萬，結果倒欠銀行37.2萬。<br />\n<br />\n還有客戶投資500萬元人民幣，22日睡醒後發現賬戶結餘為負900多萬元人民幣，頓成「千萬負翁」，還被中行連環短訊和電話催債。<br />\n<br />\n原油寶受害人鄧先生對銀行的處理極為不滿，他說：「它直接把我的錢直接扣走了。它把本金全部扣完了以後，它把你銀行裏面其它錢全部給劃走了。」<br />\n<br />\n網上傳出影片顯示，廣東江門鶴山經緯花園一名男子準備跳樓輕生，被幾個人給拉住了，很不幸最終還是悲劇收場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-04-25/3084312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-04-25%2F3084312&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=aa1dd8ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-04-25/3084312</a>"},{"pid":"5226d7a1431ded6077cf0c657c75c24e7dd152e7","tid":1988872,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be162c7ef25679131f2b108e04cf776853ee409d","tid":1988872,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"頓成「千萬負翁」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ha